                    <msContents class="lemmatic">
                        <summary> This manuscript contains part of a commentary on the Hippocratic
                            Aphorisms. The front matter attributes the text to Palladius (fl. C. 6th
                            century) although recent scholarship contests that (see Pormann et al,
                            2018). It contains commentaries on the following aphorisms: I: 1, 4, 9,
                            11, 12, 14, 16 and 17; II: 1 and 2, 9, 15, 19. </summary>

                        <msItem>
                            <title xml:lang="Eng">Commentary on the Hippocratic Aphorisms</title>
                            <title xml:lang="Ara">شرح فصول أبقراط منسوب إلى فلاذيوس</title>
